# Movie Recommendation App

A React-based movie recommendation system. This application allows users to browse popular and trending movies, view movie details, and receive personalized recommendations.

**Note:** This project uses the TMDB API. You will need to obtain an API key and replace `'YOUR_TMDB_API_KEY'` in `src/api/tmdb.js` for actual API calls to work. If no API key is provided, the application will fall back to using mock data.